column5: This was from last year.http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tFKsEp8wq5Y Heading back again this spring and can't wait!

Nice slideshow of what looked like a great family vacation. Hopefully when my daughter is older she'll accompany me on some fishing trips.I liked the assortment of fishing related fashion too, lol. I don't think I own a single fishing related T-shirt and I am not sure why. Time to change that.
Thanks for the therapy! Posts like this help with cabin fever eh!? Or... does it just make it worse?
Thanks for sharing that. I can't wait for spring.
Very nice,I never saw a person caught a fish that did't smile
